This strike mission has been an absolute nightmare.
The yellow king collapsed the main passage into the heart of the forest and he and his guard are far stronger than we anticipated.

I will have to thank the water pneumas for suggesting it.

The First Witch, the creator of the sage forest, the rider of the stars.
